<div
  style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #047857 0%, #065f46 100%); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.875rem;"
  role="banner"
  aria-label="v1 beta announcement"
>
  The beta version of Evalite v1 is now available! Install with <code
    style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-family: monospace; color: white;"
